Mujhe lagta hai ki internet par pehle se kahin zyada hamle ho rahe hain. Sarkarein ab internet se darti hain kyunki madhya purv ke kaaran unhone ise lekar apni chintayein badha di hain, aur ve ab un vyavsayik hiton ko sunne ke liye thoda adhik tayar hain jo logon ki svatantrataon ko seemit karke paisa kamaana chahte hain, lekin unhone upayogkartao ki pratikriya ko bhi dekha hai, jaise SOPA ke khilaf backlash. Mujhe lagta hai ki sarkarein agar upayogkartao ki svatantrataon se takraati hain, to ve khud hi khatre mein pad sakti hain.

Nenu bhavistunnanu internet pai ippati daka unna edaina kaalamlo kante ekkuvadiga daadulu jarugutunnayi. Prabhutvamalulu ippudu internet gurinchi bhayapadutunnayi endukante madhyaprachya sambandhita vishayalu valana avi konchem jaagrathaga unnayi mariyu ee taraha vyapara prayojanalu vyaktula svechhalanu parimitim cheyadam dwara dabbu sampadinchalaane vaaru maatallanu vinadani ki marinta siddhanga unnayi. Kani vaalu SOPA lanti pratikoopala pratispandananu kuda choosaaru. Naaku anipistunte, prabhutvamalulu viniyogadarula svechhalato poraatam chesthe, vaalu daniki pratiga shikshana pondavachu.

Enna vaazhdhal thonudhal internet-ukku ippodhu munnadi irundha kaalamthaanum periya azhuththugal thodangudhal. Aasaiyalar ippodhu internet patri bayapadugirargal, enna madhyapracchi kaaranaththaal adhuvum avargal thunaiyum konjam kadandha mudhal tharum, idharku mela theriyaanavida. Avargal thunaiyum pothuvaga vyabasaaya suvaikkarai thavira alavukku seyyum nilaivida. Kani avargal porundhal saadhana seythellavida soppa veedhugal kooda samajikkal.

‘Always on Time’ hochi American rapper Ja Rule ra duiti single, ja ja ra third studio album 'Pain is Love' ru aasi thila. Ei gaana re American R&B singer Ashanti feature hei thila ebong ei gaana ku Irv Gotti produce kari thile. Ei gaana ku Aurelius, Ja Rule, ebong Irving Lorenzo likhithile. Ei gaana duniya bhitare hit hebaare purnanga safala heithila ebong ei gaana Ashanti ra prathama Hot Number One single au Ja Rule ra dutiya hit hoithila.

‘Always on Time’ Ja Rule ka doosra single hai, jo uske teesre studio album 'Pain is Love' se tha. Is gaane mein American R&B singer Ashanti ka feature tha aur isse Irv Gotti ne produce kiya tha. Gaana likha tha Aurelius, Ja Rule aur Irving Lorenzo ne. Yeh gaana duniya bhar mein hit ho gaya aur yeh Ashanti ka pehla Hot Number One single tha aur Ja Rule ka doosra.

‘Always on Time’ ane gaana, American rapper Ja Rule dawara pettina renduva single, tana third studio album 'Pain is Love' nundi ochindhi. Ee gaana lo American R&B singer Ashanti feature chesindi, mariyu ee gaana ni Irv Gotti produce chesadu. Ee gaana ni Aurelius, Ja Rule mariyu Irving Lorenzo raasaru. Ee gaana prapancham lo hit ayyindi mariyu ee gaana Ashanti ki modati Hot Number One single aithe Ja Rule ki renduva hit.

‘Always on Time’ enna kaana, American rapper Ja Rule-udaiya rantuva single, avanudaiya third studio album 'Pain is Love' inda varum. Ithu kaana, American R&B singer Ashanti feature aagindha, matrum ithu Irv Gotti producer aayirundha. Ithu kaana, Aurelius, Ja Rule, matrum Irving Lorenzo ezhudhi irundha. Ithu kaana ulagam thodangiya hit aayidha, matrum ithu Ashanti-udaiya mudhal Hot Number One single aagidha, Ja Rule-udaiya rantuva hit.

‘Always on Time’ shì American rapper Ja Rule de dì èr zh? g?, láizì t? de dì s?n zh? studio album 'Pain is Love'. Zhè sh?u g? y?u American R&B singer Ashanti c?nji?, ér zhè sh?u g? shì yóu Irv Gotti chéngb?o de. Zhè sh?u g? shì yóu Aurelius, Ja Rule hé Irving Lorenzo xi? de. Zhè sh?u g? chéngwéi quánqiú dào h?i de rèmén g?, y? shì Ashanti de dì y? gè Hot Number One single, y? shì Ja Rule de dì èr gè.

‘Always on Time’ wa American rapper Ja Rule no daini single de, kare no sanbanme no studio album 'Pain is Love' kara deshita. Kono songu ni wa American R&B singer Ashanti ga f?ch? sare, sono songu wa Irv Gotti ni yotte seich? saremashita. Kono songu wa Aurelius, Ja Rule, to Irving Lorenzo ni yotte kaita mono desu. Kono songu wa sekai-ch? de hit o kiki, Ashanti no saisho no Hot Number One single to, Ja Rule no daini hit to natta.

a memorial to the achievements of the mwsa currently stands on the lawn of the minnesota state capitol and is known as the minnesota woman suffrage memorial
MWSA ra safalatara smarakanka eka smarakabarana Minnesota rajya capitol ra bagicha re sthita achhi ebong ta ku Minnesota Mahila Matadana Smarakanka rupe jana jae
MWSA ki safaltayon ka ek smarak abhi Minnesota State Capitol ke bagiche par sthit hai aur ise Minnesota Mahila Matdan Smarak ke roop mein jaana jaata hai.
MWSA yoka safalatalu samarpinchina oka smarakamu ippudu Minnesota State Capitol loni bagichalo undi, adhi Minnesota Mahila Matadan Smarakam ani piluvabadutundi.

MWSA inri varach cheyyum udhavi sammanam oru smarakaththarvam ippodhu Minnesota State Capitol thottaththil irundhu varugirathu, adhu Minnesota Mahila Votting Smarakaththarvamaaga arindhidappadugirathu.

MWSA no seika e no kinen no tame no kinenhi ga genzai, Minnesota sh? govenment no ry? no ni arimasu, soshite Minnesota josei senkyo kinenhi to shite shirareteimasu.
a photograph of his son x tecumseh clark born october   was featured on the cover art of canadian electronic music band crystal castles second eponymous album in
Tankara putra X Tecumseh Clark jaha October re janma heithila, tankara eka photo Canadian electronic music band Crystal Castles ra dwitiya eponymous album ra cover art re dekha jaithila.
Unke putra X Tecumseh Clark, jinka janm October mein hua tha, unki ek tasveer Canadian electronic music band Crystal Castles ke doosre eponymous album ke cover art par dekhi gayi thi.
Aayana kumarudu X Tecumseh Clark, yavariki October lo janminchinaaru, aayana photo Canadian electronic music band Crystal Castles madhya eponymous album cover lo kanipinchindi.
Avargalin magan X Tecumseh Clark, ivar October-il pirandha, avar oru padam Canadian electronic music band Crystal Castles in irandaavathu eponymous album cover-il irundhadhu.
T? de érzi X Tecumseh Clark, ch?sh?ng zài Shíyuè, t? de yì zh?ng zhàopiàn ch?xiàn zài Ji?nádà diànz? y?nyuè tuán Crystal Castles dì èr zh?ng tóngmíng zhu?njí de f?ngmiàn yìshù.
Kare no musuko X Tecumseh Clark wa, 10-gatsu ni umareta, kare no shashin wa Kanada no denshi ongaku bando Crystal Castles no 2-banme no jiko teiki album no kab? ?to ni t?j? shimashita.

a talk by takis fotopoulos about the internationalization of the capitalist market economy and the project of inclusive democracy a talk given by takis fotopoulos at the university of vermont in  followed by a discussion in which murray bookchin dan chodorkoff and others take part video in  parts retrieved  january

Takis Fotopoulos dwara antarjatikarana o capitalistic market economy ra inclusive democracy upare ekta alochana University of Vermont re heithila, jaha pare Murray Bookchin, Dan Chodorkoff ebong anya loka samil hela. Ei video parts re January re upalabdha heithila.

Takis Fotopoulos dwara kapitalist bazar arthvyavastha ke antarashtriyakaran aur inclusive loktantra par ek vyakhyan University of Vermont mein diya gaya, jiske baad Murray Bookchin, Dan Chodorkoff aur anya logon ne charcha mein bhaag liya. Yeh video parts mein January mein prapt hua.

Takis Fotopoulos dvara antarjatikarana mariyu kapitalist market economy gurinchi inclusive democracy pai mata University of Vermont lo icharu. Taruvata Murray Bookchin, Dan Chodorkoff mariyu inka charchalo palgunaru. Ee video parts lo January lo dorikindi.

Takis Fotopoulos avargal kapitalist market economy-yin ulagam pughalchi matrum inclusive democracy patri University of Vermont-il oru pesal nadathinar. Pinbu Murray Bookchin, Dan Chodorkoff matrum matra ulagangalum kalandhu oru alochanai nadathinaargal. Intha video January-il pagirkkapattathu.

Takis Fotopoulos zài Vermont dàxué ji?nglùn z?b?n zh?yì shìch?ng j?ngjì de guójì huà hé b?ohán xìng mínzh? jìhuà. Suíhòu Murray Bookchin, Dan Chodorkoff hé qít? rén c?nji?le t?olùn. Zhège shìpín y? j?ng yú Y?yuè huòdé.

Takis Fotopoulos wa kapitalisuto shij? keizai no kokusai-ka to h?setsuteki minshushugi no purojekuto ni tsuite Vermont Daigaku de k?en o okonai, sono nochi Murray Bookchin, Dan Chodorkoff oyobi hoka no hitobito ga sanka suru giron ga okonawareta. Kono bideo wa ichi-gatsu ni shutsugen shimashita.
Zuìhòu y?zhí de bìngzhì huì jiézhì shí, n?xìng sùf? hé f?n p?lì t?ng de bìnglì y?q? mièb?o.
aberllefenni is a village in the south of gwynedd wales it lies in the historic county of merionethshiresir feirionnydd in the valley of the afon dulas
Aberllefenni ekati grama jo Gwynedd, Wales ra dakshin bhagare achhi. Eha itihasik Merionethshire/Sir Feirionnydd jilar madhya achhi, ebong Afon Dulas upatyakare sthita.
Aberllefenni ek gaon hai jo Gwynedd, Wales ke dakshin mein sthit hai. Yah itihaasik Merionethshire/Sir Feirionnydd zila mein hai aur Afon Dulas ghaati mein sthit hai.
Aberllefenni ane gramam Gwynedd, Wales dakshina bhagam lo undi. Idi charitraka Merionethshire/Sir Feirionnydd jilalo mariyu Afon Dulas gutta lo undi.
Aberllefenni ennum oru gramam Gwynedd, Wales in thekku pagudhi-il ullathu. Idhu varalartriya Merionethshire/Sir Feirionnydd maavattathilum Afon Dulas pallathakku-ilum irukkirathu.
Aberllefenni shì wèil? yú Gwynedd, Wales nánbù de y? gè c?nzhu?ng. T? zuòluò yú lìsh? sh?ng Merionethshire/Sir Feirionnydd, bìng wèiyú Afon Dulas xiág? zh?ng.
Aberllefenni wa Gwynedd, Wales no minami ni aru mura desu. Sore wa rekishiteki na Merionethshire/Sir Feirionnydd ni zaisuru, Afon Dulas tani ni ichi shiteimasu.
